    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sanctae et individuae Trinitatis. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/79">Hugo</persName> et <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/72">Lotharius</persName> divina favente clementia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">reges</rs>. Si sanctis ac venerabilibus locis ea
                        quae ab antecessoribus nostris collata sunt corroborare studuerimus, et de
                        his quae nostri iuris sunt concedere satagimus, aeternae vitae emolumentum
                        adipisci ac presentis status soliditatem propensius augmentari non
                        titubamus. Idcirco omnium fidelium sanctae Dei Ecclesiae nostrorumque
                        presentium ac futurorum industria noverit, <rs key="#Abbots">abbatem</rs> et
                            <rs key="#Monks">monachos</rs> in <rs key="#Monasteries">coenobio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Houses #Curtes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Decima #Public_exactions #Angaria #Churches #Monasteries #Cells/hermitages #Abbots #Monks #Royal_slave"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/301">domini et salvatoris nostri Iesu
                            Christi</orgName> militantes in <placeName ref="#places/737">monte
                            Amiate</placeName> nobis lacrimabiliter protulisse, quod famis ac
                        nuditatis indigentia ibidem Deo servire non possent, eo quod <rs
                            key="#Curtes">cortes</rs> et <rs key="#Cells/hermitages">cellae</rs>,
                        quae a predecessoribus nostris ad sumptum eorum collatae sunt, a pravis
                        fu[i]ssent distractae hominibus. Nos quidem pro Dei amore animarumque
                        nostrarum remedio, quoniam idem cenobium in nostram devenerat potestatem ac
                        proprietatem, res et predia, quae a nostris precessoribus collata sunt et
                        confirmata ac corroborata, confirmare et corroborare studuimus, et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >de nostri iuris proprietate in monachorum sumptum cortes et cellas
                            contulimus</rs>, quatenus sedulo orationes pro nobis <rs key="#motherOf"
                            >matreque</rs> nostra <persName key="#motherOf" ref="#people/1524"
                            >Berta</persName> ibidem ad Dominum dirigantur. Igitur cortes et cellas,
                            <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">massaricia</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">sortes</rs>, <rs key="#Royal_slave"
                            >familiamque utriusque sexus</rs> quae hactenus tenuerunt, omniaque
                        precepta ab antecessoribus nostris conlata, omniaque instrumenta confirmamus
                        pleniterque corroboramus; et quoniam prefatum cenobium in nostram devenit
                        potestatem et proprietatem, ex quae a pravis ablata sunt hominibus et alia
                        quibus indigentiam explere valeant, in usum fratrum per hoc nostrum
                        preceptum concedimus, donamus atque largimur, videlicet <rs
                            key="#Cells/hermitages">cellam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            >Sacti Benedicti</orgName>, <rs key="#Curtes">curtem</rs> de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/334">Palea</geogName>, cellam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/303">Sancti Stephani in <placeName
                                ref="#places/757">[Monti]clo</placeName></orgName>, et cellam
                            <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/302">Sanctae Mariae in Lamulas</orgName>,
                        corticellam de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/331">Mustia</geogName>, [nec]non et corticellam de
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/335">Titinano</geogName>, et in
                            <placeName>Cerri</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Angaria">angariales</rs>, et <rs key="#Curtes">curticellam</rs> in
                            <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/761"><geogName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#estates/2315">Fereniano</geogName></placeName>, nec non et
                            <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/308">cellam Sancti Salvatoris</orgName> in
                            <placeName ref="#places/762">vale Racana</placeName>, et curticellam de
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/332">Cuniclo</geogName> cum ipso <rs key="#Houses"
                            >caiolo</rs> de Porciano, et cellam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1455">Sancti Stephani</orgName> in <placeName
                            ref="#places/430">Terquino</placeName>, seu et cellam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                                ><geogName ref="#estates/2334">Sancti Severi</geogName></orgName>
                        super <rs key="#Lakes">lacum</rs> cum ipsa corticella de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/333">Besantio</geogName>, cellam etiam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            >Sancti Miniati</orgName>, nec non et cellam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            >Sanctae Mariae de Valeriano</orgName> cum ipsis rebus de
                            <placeName>Curticiole</placeName>, cum omnibus adiacentiis et
                        pertinentiis earum, atque cortem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2309">Sanctae Mariae ad Offena</geogName>, et curticellam
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2310">Sancti Simeonis</geogName> et <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2311">Sanctum Petrum in Cervaria</geogName>, cum omnibus
                        rebus et familiis ad eas in integrum pertinentibus vel respicientibus.
                        Denique etiam concedimus predicto cenobio omnia <rs key="#Decima"
                            >decima</rs>, frea et iudiciaria et omnem compositionem et <rs
                            key="#Public_exactions">exibitionem</rs> publicam ex omnibus manentibus
                        predicti monasterii ob remedium animarum nostrarum matrisque nostrae in usum
                        peregrinorum ad portam monasterii clamantium, precipimus etiam et statuimus,
                        ut deinceps in futurum haec nostra confirmatio atque donatio a posteris
                        nostris inconvulsa maneat et inlibata, et ut nullus dux, marchio, comes,
                        vicecomes aut ulla regni nostri magna parvaque persona in domos vel res
                        predicti cenobii violentiam inferat aut famulos flagellare vel angariare
                        presumat, neque de predictis rebus ullam minorationem facere satagat; sed
                        liceat abbatem sanctamque congregationem predictas cortes et cellas cum
                        eorum integritatibus tenere, omnium inquie[tudi]ne remota. Si quis igitur
                        hoc nostrum preceptum vìolare temptaverit, sciat se compositurum <rs>auri
                            optimi libras centum</rs>, <rs key="#Camera_regis">medietatem kamerae
                            nostrae</rs> et <rs key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem
                            sanctae congregationi predicti cenobii</rs>. Quod ut veius credatur
                        diligentiusque observetur, manibus propriis roborantes anuli nostri
                        inpressione subter iussimus insigniri. Signa serenissimorum (MF) (MF) domni
                        Hugonis et Lotharii regum. <persName key="#Chaplain" ref="#people/1535"
                            >Giseprandus</persName> domnorum regum <rs key="#Chaplain"
                            >capellanus</rs> regi iussu recognovi et subscripsi. Data III non.
                        octub., anno dominicae incarnationis DCCCCXXXVII, regni vero domni Hugonis
                        regis XII, filii [ve]ro eius Lotharii item regis VII, indictione XI. Actum
                        ad <placeName>pontem Andria</placeName>. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
